162
00:06:55.326 --> 00:06:59.395
- She runs the store with her husband.
- Okay. come on.

163
00:06:59.464 --> 00:07:01.430
- And they both owe me money!
- No. turn around.

164
00:07:01.499 --> 00:07:03.866
No. you're the cops from before;
you're the ones

165
00:07:03.935 --> 00:07:06.347
