- He could have killed that woman.

166
00:07:06.371 --> 00:07:08.549
- Why don't you do your job already. huh?
- You know what?

167
00:07:08.573 --> 00:07:10.807
I want your names.
I want your badge numbers. Now.

168
00:07:13.130 --> 00:07:14.221
