196
00:08:06.307 --> 00:08:09.441
Okay. you know what I mean--
like. we're not responsible.

197
00:08:09.510 --> 00:08:11.884
Mm-hmm. And how about
you in the back?

198
00:08:11.885 --> 00:08:14.452
