218
00:09:04.871 --> 00:09:08.607
Oh. it's just a little
scratchy throat. that's all.

219
00:09:08.675 --> 00:09:09.941
Something going around?

220
00:09:10.010 --> 00:09:13.678
No. it's. um...

221
